WEBVTT

00:06.549 --> 00:07.280
Wake-up Call

00:08.311 --> 00:11.975
It's something that makes a person understand a problem or danger.

00:13.441 --> 00:18.493
The rising sea level is a wake-up call for us to do something about climate change.

00:21.144 --> 00:25.265
The increasing crime rate is a wake-up call for people to stay alert.

00:26.622 --> 00:30.451
The number of people with lung disease is a wake-up call for us...

00:30.811 --> 00:32.726
...about the dangers of smoking.

